text: Silvia Martínez (born 22 September 1974) is a Spanish gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Spain Category:Gymnasts at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Madrid
